snippet: Top-seeded Jo-Wilfried Tsonga overcame a sloppy second set to beat Daniel Brands of Germany and reach the quarterfinals of the Erste Bank Open in Vienna.
abstract: Top-seeded Jo-Wilfried Tsonga reaches quarterfinals of Erste Bank Open in Vienna; other tennis news noted.
